episodes.title: A Cult or Divine Intervention? | The Heartbreaking Story of Elizabeth Struhs
episodes.description:
January 2022, 8 year old Elizabeth Struhs suffered for 5 days through a 100 percent preventable death. While her Mother and Father, along with members of their cult-like church The Saints, stood by and watched. Join us and Elizabeth's sister Jayde in fighting for justice for Elizabeth!
